text: Volusenus is a name that may refer to: *Gaius Volusenus (fl. mid-1st century BCE), distinguished military officer of the Roman Republic who served under Julius Caesar for ten years, during the Gallic Wars and the civil war of the 40s *Florentius Volusenus (c. 1504 – 1546 or 1547), Scottish humanist
title: Volusenus
